{"tid":1350034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對付白衫軍既辦法好簡單 個個都做到","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T00:56:00.000Z","uid":10905,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48bd7ef16797cfaf3a18c3f09606ec9019ac26d7","tid":1350034,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"就係黑警上身<br />\n<br />\n點解黑警咁撚串可以係咁迫係咁打<br />\n點解成日都有義士落單<br />\n就係因為我地驚我地退<br />\n<br />\n當對方知你會退<br />\n佢求其搵幾個速龍出黎鳩揮下支棍就夠推走你地<br />\n佢地口氣就會更大<br />\n亦愈搞會愈大<br />\n因為知你唔會還手<br />\n<br />\n但當有一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自衛</span>還擊打到對方爆曬缸<br />\n我就唔信個個都仲係咁大聲<br />\n佢地就會退<br />\n<br />\n所以下次大家諗下d速龍d警察點打鳩你地<br />\n你用番佢果招<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自衛</span>就得<br />\n<br />\n心態大於一切"},{"pid":"687722187f29ac3c477d9c4725891bc7272816cc","tid":1350034,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eade6484d0ec4bb70c257fad18795907ea7e266c","tid":1350034,"uid":34415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bb96e40662d6a3c6d965246f57721c847b464f7","tid":1350034,"uid":283972,"like":1,"disl